          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Philoxenus of Mabūg. Fragments of the Commentaries of Philoxenus of Mabūg on the Gospels of S. Matthew and S. Luke. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 3 items.</note>
